.TH "LIGHTNING-FORWARD" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-forward \- forwarded-HTLC introspection (FEAT-188)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning forward
[\fIsubcommand\fR] [\fIargs\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.nf
lightning forward — forwarded-HTLC introspection (FEAT-188).

Wraps clightning's `listforwards`. Routing nodes use this
to see what went through them and what they earned.

Subcommands:
  list [--since <date>] [--status settled|failed|local_failed|offered]
  stats                                  totals: msats / fees / success rate
.fi
.SH USAGE
.nf
usage: lightning forward <subcommand>

   list [--since <date>] [--status settled|failed|local_failed|offered]
   stats                              totals: msat / fees / success rate
.fi
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.BR lightning (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Part of the \fBlightning\fR educational Lightning Network frontend.
